{"tid":1702373,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 勇武文宣必須全面進場連儂牆","createTime":"2019-11-09T16:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T06:52:18.000Z","uid":190579,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a125e758f3ff0b5dbc4dc85053bc08b79e3c3de","tid":1702373,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:04:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TLDR：<br />\n所有勇武連登仔<br />\n去連儂場發佈勇武思想</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n連儂場文宣可以好簡單<br />\n白紙大黑字就夠<br />\n其實唔難<br />\n<br />\n好多和理非都好撚嬲<br />\n但因為佢哋天性善良<br />\n唔會諗點樣最有效地傷害敵人<br />\n結果就一係只能繼續做嬲撚<br />\n一係就喺毫無準備下上前線<br />\n送頭了<br />\n這是不好的<br />\n<br />\n而家連農場99.99%文宣係和理非向<br />\n叫人出嚟<br />\n但出到嚟做咩又唔撚講<br />\n結果又係上演每周劇本<br />\n尻企食煙潰逃<br />\n最後唯有番屋企嬲嬲<br />\n<br />\n至於日日口勇既連登仔<br />\n就從來唔會跳出連登<br />\n去連農場宣揚佢既勇武思想<br />\n這也是不好的<br />\n<br />\n正面例子：職業圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kp2oUJ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKp2oUJ0.png&h=362451d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n取自<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2964107673602745&amp;id=1799974313349426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2964107673602745%26id%3D1799974313349426&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSphSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=27b8df9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2964107673602745&amp;id=1799974313349426</a>"},{"pid":"8be3e821b2b89348cd4f86fd6836563ffc50225c","tid":1702373,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:04:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f02fdf14e7f73f74ee8856dae8a9c25c585fa923","tid":1702373,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46c2b6271a3b4dadb8453b04865e091842319fa0","tid":1702373,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T16:05:0